s Trins cheek then scurries to the door,but then looks back at Trinity. "Hun,you wont mind watching Brook,while I go see May would you?" Grins already knowing the answer. " Alrighty then." Blows a kiss,then scurries out of the hut."  Feeling all chipper being a new mom and all. <br>
